snippet.title: 《Cat God Ranch》Game Trailer — Lead a group of funny animals to offer tribute to the Cat God
snippet.description: 《Cat God Ranch》 is a roguelite card-building game with a fun animal theme.Players take on the role of a ranch administrator, strategically building a lineup of small animals and earning enough coins to offer tribute to the Cat God within a specified deadline.
